{
  "stem": "27748.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not so much why, but how.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know at what point you want to get into that.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] when I went to Israel much later, in 1972, when I thought I was emigrating to Israel-- I'm jumping ahead now-- I had to confront the matter of learning a language.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I think she knew my story.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So she was-- she herself, then as I said, was a Quaker, and had a PhD.D.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But she was very active in what was then world federalism, of trying to promote a world government, a sane world government.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She was very active.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She was very active in politics.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There were senators-- Sam Ervin, of the Watergate fame, was one of her boys.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She'd tell him what to do.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He would come to her house.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She would tell him how he should run his life.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he would respectfully listen.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, I mean, there were many people with whom she kept in personal touch, and bombarded them with letters, and phone calls, and invite them to her house.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they would come.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She had a very strong personality.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She was a tiny framed little woman, but very strong.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So, anyway, there, too, I was exposed to the idea of making something of yourself.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so, for instance, she made a lot of herself.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "For instance, she was in nutrition.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And at that time, let's say in terms of bread that people eat, white flour was the thing, where she felt the white flour had all the goodness out of it.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So she decided, and made up a formula, for whole wheat flour.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And nobody would manufacture it.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
